	<h1 class="title">公司被挂牌出售时，手里的用户数据也会跟着被卖掉</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name"> Natasha Singer, Jeremy B. Merrillj</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-07-02 13:00:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/11439/medium/11439.jpg?1436639592" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="11439" data-title="《公司被挂牌出售时，手里的用户数据也会跟着被卖掉》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/11439/medium/11439.jpg?1436639592" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/11439.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
